Package: ragent
Title: Simple R Agent Using Local LLM
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Demonstrates a simple agent model in R using local LLM through
    Ollama's API directly. The package provides basic agent functionality
    for task execution and reasoning, using llama3.2:1b for simple tasks and
    deepseek-r1:1.5b for complex reasoning.
